{"tid":1588570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"推到612基金回應","createTime":"2019-09-23T01:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T01:47:10.000Z","uid":61886,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"08d2697115e9c16741998c5934b6c98bd072115e","tid":1588570,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:21:11.000Z","msg":"睇返612份報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1U8U6174kRffycKjWcNALjKqzKNco3xxIPws2FzN1krI/htmlview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1U8U6174kRffycKjWcNALjKqzKNco3xxIPws2FzN1krI%2Fhtmlview&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly82proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=edf559ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1U8U6174kRffycKjWcNALjKqzKNco3xxIPws2FzN1krI/htmlview</a><br />\n<br />\n有個位希望612基金可以解釋下<br />\n<br />\n睇返份report<br />\n醫療批左50萬 (69人)<br />\n緊急經濟支援60萬 (55人)<br />\n法律費用資助11萬 (12人)<br />\n借出保釋金20萬 (27人)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/41w6r7F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F41w6r7F.png&h=87a59933&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先唔討論cover既人數點解咁少<br />\n<br />\n最底項目支援<br />\n有一個分頁再有講<br />\n616音響開支 28萬<br />\n623音響開支 2萬8<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ufPPpUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FufPPpUk.png&h=ef31de09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n批音響唔係問題<br />\n但支援補捕/受傷人士得百幾萬<br />\n音響你就批左30萬？<br />\n<br />\n我諗無人會覺得講得通架嘛<br />\n<br />\n依個批錢既方向同做法好影響我再捐唔捐錢比612基金<br />\n<br />\nPS 如果有解釋過 我wow左既請唔好推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c77e30aa8c6bbf8d35e63bedcfc6a3c03a2fd3b","tid":1588570,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:22:00.000Z","msg":"音響係21萬同2萬8 <br />\n打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebbf46a33a3fd3f8bf9111587eb4d86c39beb7a","tid":1588570,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:22:10.000Z","msg":"一個月前佢話冇咩人搵佢幫手"},{"pid":"ba3bd8935013ebe20316b7bfe08c7fd674822432","tid":1588570,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:23:39.000Z","msg":"醫療有要求既話應該都有批<br />\n緊急經濟支援 我諗大家都知佢地點都唔肯拎 <br />\n得55人申請<br />\n法律費用資助 一日未上庭一日都未用到"},{"pid":"7df15f29ad3c0f8db2a90aa205af912ab8f053d7","tid":1588570,"uid":403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3787a5b7bd7745babf1f240845beb784c45ccc7","tid":1588570,"uid":204571,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:26:09.000Z","msg":"612其實唔係太差 利申非打手<br />\n我早幾日真係走頭無路去申請緊急經濟援助<br />\n3到4日就批左 仲問有無其他野幫手"},{"pid":"2e27e8fbad64b8616c655b31fa3154de08630e16","tid":1588570,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T01:47:10.000Z","msg":"兩個唔係可以類比既數目喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢按單據按需要去批錢，無得決定批多d批少d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n暫時未有人實名指控612唔批錢，應該要信住先"}]}